div.bibl: Otthon, Mar. 16, 1930. IGNATIO IZSAK TO RUN FOR COUNTY COMMISSIONER.

body.p: p.2...Ignacio Izsak will run for the office of County Commissioner, in the primaries Apr. 8. The committee working in Mr. Izsak's interest, will meet Mar. 18, Tuesday evening, at the hall above the Immigration State Bank, 343 W. North Ave. All those who wish to aid the committee, in their efforts, are asked to come to the meeting place at the appointed time.
